### [Component: Release Packet Generation]

We will configure the packet generator to write to the tenant-isolated workspace and include the required gate verification terms.

#### [MODIFY] [generate-release-packet.cjs](file:///d:/Projects/Prism/scripts/generate-release-packet.cjs)
- Update the default output path of the release candidate to write to BOTH `prism-output/releases` and the workspace's releases directory `workspacePath("artifacts", "releases")` dynamically by reading preferences.
- Set the generated `governance-path-report.md` to explicitly include the rollback rehearsal terms `"timeout"`, `"revoke"`, and `"pass"`.
- Set the generated `release-packet-manifest.md` to explicitly include the staging qualification phrase `"packet complete: yes"`.

